summary: SummaryLancôme Lip Idôle Lip Shaper is a creamy, soft matte lip pencil that is waterproof and provides up to 8H wear. This lip liner pencil is blendable, rich in color, and infused with ceramides & jojoba oil.
details: DetailsFeaturesThis lasting lip liner glides on effortlessly without tugging, allowing for instantly shaped & contoured lipsBenefitsUp to 8H wearNo tug application, lip pencil formula glides on effortlesslyLips look shaped and contouredItem 2626306How To UseTo apply lip liner, outline lips by following your natural lip line starting at the cupids bow.To create the look of full lips, try overlined lips by drawing over the edge of your natural lip line to create your desired shape.Pro-Tips:Use finger to blend to add color and softness to overall lipFor more color impact, gradually fill in entire lip using Lip Idôle Lip ShaperFill in lips using the matching Lip Idôle Squalane-12 Butterglow shade for 24H hydration and instant color & shine, or customize your look mixing and matching any of the 12 shades of Lip Idôle Lip Shaper and 8 shades of Lip Idôle Squalane-12 Butterglow.IngredientsIsododecane, CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, Synthetic Wax, Polybutene, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Mica, Isoamyl Laurate, Silica, Sucrose Tetrastearate Triacetate, Hydrogenated Jojoba Oil, Cetearyl Behenate, CI 77491 / Iron Oxides, CI 77742 / Manganese Violet, CI 77492 / Iron Oxides, Ceramide Np, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details

faceoff_positive.comments:
Picture this: you're getting ready for a summer soirée, ready to dazzle with your killer outfit, but you realize something's missing – that perfect lip liner to tie it all together. Enter the Lip Idole Lip Liner. This bad boy goes on smoother than your favorite pick-up line (and trust me, it's much more reliable).

First off, let's talk texture. If you've ever spread room temperature butter on warm toast, you know exactly what to expect. This lip liner glides on with such ease, it practically moonwalks across your lips. Seriously, even the clumsiest of us can achieve a flawless line without looking like we let a toddler take a crack at our makeup.

Now, longevity. This liner stays put longer than a stubborn stain on your favorite white shirt. I'm talking all-day wear – it's so committed, it could teach your ex a thing or two about sticking around. Kiss-proof? Absolutely. I tested it through multiple iced lattes, a few cheeky cocktails, and a vigorous make-out session (for science, of course). Not a smudge in sight.

And the color – oh, the color. It's the perfect summer hue, bright enough to be noticed but subtle enough to wear to that daytime BBQ. I got so many compliments, I'm considering making this liner my new best friend (sorry, Maddie).

After trying it, I'm convinced I need every shade. I mean, if one color can perform this well, imagine what a whole rainbow can do! I'm about to start a collection that'll make the Skittles bag look monochromatic.

In conclusion, if you're looking for a lip liner that's smoother than your best one-liner, longer-lasting than a reality TV series, and a color to make your summer sizzle – Lip Idole Lip Liner is your new holy grail. Just don't blame me when your partner gets jealous of how much you're raving about it!
faceoff_positive.headline: I cant get enough of Lip Idole Lip Liners

faceoff_negative.comments: I wasn't a big fan of this product. When I received the product I couldn't get the cap off and ended up breaking off the tip of the lip liner. I received the color mahogany mom. I was searching on the lip liner to find a sharpener but was disappointed to find that there was none so I had to dig out one of my old sharpeners. And here's where the problem starts the lip liner is so soft and creamy it feels almost impossible to sharpen. Certain products are like that where yes they are extremely creamy and they go on smooth but it doesn't help when you need to sharpen the product the color payoff is great the shade is beautiful kind of fall Vibes purpley brownish color. It reminds me of a reason and I really like those colors. But I could not see myself paying for this product because I feel like I have some quality control issues. I received this product for free in exchange for an honest review
